metadata.name: A New Day
metadata.description: This was a piece inspired by [this instagram post](https://www.instagram.com/p/CZuxDjdPuGn/). It's a post full of hope and possibilities now that her abusive conservatorship is over, she actually has the freedom to go. In so many ways, Britney Spear's story is an allegory for the oppressive patriarchal system we women are subjected to, while the corrupted conservatorship is a concrete manifestation of that oppression. Perhaps as she has now gained her freedom, one day all of us will too.
